title: Alex.Jones.Show.2008.06.20-chakra71
description:
Open Line Friday. Stand-in host Jason Bermas takes your calls and discusses the issues of the day. An encore presentation of Alex's Ralph Nader and Dennis Kucinich interviews will air in the last hour.

I split the hours up into different tracks and added the show description in the directory to make for easier archiving.  Let me know if there are any problems with this format.
